dc_title_s: Caribbean Sea, Netherlands Antilles, Bonaire (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. "From a Netherlands chart in 1986." Place names in Danish with glossary in English. "Copyright 1996 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Insets: A. Kralendijk Roadstead. Scale 1:25,070 -- B. Goto Oil Terminal (Bopec Terminal). Scale 1:20,074 -- C. Salt Pier. Scale 1;10,007 -- D. Kralendijk Pier. Scale 1:10,039. Map no.24461. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
